<CENTER><H3>
Evaluating Prolongation in Extended Tonality</H3>
<a href="http://www-student.furman.edu/users/r/rkelley/" target="_top">Robert T. Kelley</a><p>
</CENTER>

<HR>

<P class="firstline">Here you will find my paper on prolongation in post-functional music.  The research presented here comes from my <a href="http://garnet.acns.fsu.edu/~rtk1218/dissertation.htm">dissertation work</a>.  The analytical model introduced in this paper is used to investigate the music of Ravel (specifically, "Ondine" from <i>Gaspard de la Nuit</I>), but may be applied to other neo-tonal musical repertoires.  Feel free to contact me about my work: &lt;<script>

